    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Locations where human activities once took place and some form of material evidence has been left behind, particularly sites where evidence of past activity is being or has been investigated using the discipline of archaeology.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
